@@TJvCustomBox
<GROUP TJvCustomBox>
Summary
  Base control for buttoned edit controls.
Description
  TJvCustomBox is a base control for edit controls with buttons. It provides separated options for
  the button and the edit as well as an method to simulate a button click.

  Never instantiate an instance of this control but rather use one of it's descendants.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomBox.BtnClick
Summary
  Responds to clicking the button.
Description
  BtnClick is called when the user clicks the button.

  The base class does nothing. Descendants should override this method to provide functionality for
  the button.
Parameters
  Sender - Reference to the control generating the event. This can be either the internal button or
           Self.
See Also
  Button, Execute
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomBox.Button
Summary
  Holds the button settings.
Description
  Button holds the settings for the internal button control.
See Also
  Edit, TJvCustomButtonOptions
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomBox.Edit
Summary
  Holds the edit settings.
Description
  Edit holds the settings for the internal edit control.
See Also
  Button, TJvCustomEditOptions
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomBox.EditChange
Summary
  Responds to changes in the edit control.
Description
  EditChange is called when the text in the edit control changes.
Parameters
  Sender - Reference to the edit control. 
See Also
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomBox.Execute
Summary
  Simulates clicking the button.
Description
  Execute simulates the user clicking the button. It does so by executing BtnClick(Self).
See Also
  BtnClick
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomBox.GetButton
Summary
  Retrieves a reference to the internal button.
Description
  GetButton retrieves a reference to the internal TSpeedButton.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomBox.GetEdit
Summary
  Retrieves a reference to the internal edit control.
Description
  GetEdit retrieves a reference to the internal TEdit.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions
<GROUP TJvCustomBox>
  Class to hold the button options in.
Description
  TJvCustomButtonOptions is a class that holds the options and settings for the speed button of a
  TJvCustomBox descendant. An instance of this class is automatically created and retrievable
  through the <LINK TJvCustomBox.Button, Button> property of the control.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Create
Summary
  Instantiates the button options class.
Description
  Create will instantiate and initialize the button options class.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox, Destroy
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Destroy
Summary
  Disposes of the button options.
Description
  Destroy will dispose of the button options instance.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox, Create
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Caption
Summary
  Caption of the button.
Description
  Caption is the text caption of the button.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Changed
Summary
  Called when settings have changed.
Description
  Changes is called whenever a setting or option has changed. If a handler has been assigned to the
  OnChanged event, it will be called.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox, OnChanged
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Cursor
Summary
  The cursor for the speed button when the mouse hovers over it.
Description
  Cursor is the cursor to show when the mouse hovers over the speed button.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Enabled
