See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Flat
Summary
  Determines if the button is flat.
Description
  Flat indicates if the speed button is drawn in a flat look or not.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Font
Summary
  The font for the speed button.
Description
  Font is the font for the speed button caption.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Glyph
Summary
  The image to show on the button.
Description
  Glyph can be set to a bitmap object containing the image to show on the button. The bitmap can
  contain up to 4 images following the same rules as TSpeedButton.Glyph.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.GlyphChanged
Summary
  Responds to changed in the glyph property.
Description
