See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Transparent
Summary
  Determines if the button is transparent.
Description
  Transparent determines if the speed button is drawn transparently.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomButtonOptions.Width
Summary
  The width of the button.
Description
  Width indicates the width of the speed button.
See Also
  TJvCustomBox
